Require Import Reals Psatz.
From Flocq Require Import Core Operations Relative Plus_error.

Section Theory.

Variable emin : Z.
Variable prec : Z.
Context {Hprec : Prec_gt_0 prec}.

Notation fexp := (FLT_exp emin prec).

Definition Bmin := bpow radix2 (emin + prec - 1).

Definition hombnd (m M u v : R) (b B : float radix2) :=
  (0 <= F2R b)%R /\ (1 <= F2R B)%R /\
  ((Bmin <= m)%R -> (Rabs (u - v) <= F2R b * M)%R /\ (Rabs v <= F2R B * M)%R).


emin, prec:Z
Hprec:Prec_gt_0 prec
forall (m M1 M2 u v : R) (b B : float radix2),
(M1 <= M2)%R ->
hombnd m M1 u v b B -> hombnd m M2 u v b B


emin, prec:Z
Hprec:Prec_gt_0 prec
forall (m M1 M2 u v : R) (b B : float radix2),
(M1 <= M2)%R ->
hombnd m M1 u v b B -> hombnd m M2 u v b B

Hprec:Prec_gt_0 prec
m, M1, M2, u, v:R
b, B:float radix2
HM:(M1 <= M2)%R
H1:(0 <= F2R b)%R
H2:(1 <= F2R B)%R
H:(Bmin <= m)%R ->
(Rabs (u - v) <= F2R b * M1)%R /\
(Rabs v <= F2R B * M1)%R
hombnd m M2 u v b B

emin, prec:Z
Hprec:Prec_gt_0 prec
forall (m M u1 v1 : R) (b1 B1 : float radix2)
  (u2 v2 : R) (b2 B2 : float radix2),
hombnd m M u1 v1 b1 B1 ->
hombnd m M u2 v2 b2 B2 ->
hombnd m M (u1 + u2) (v1 + v2) (Fplus b1 b2)
  (Fplus B1 B2)


emin, prec:Z
Hprec:Prec_gt_0 prec

  (u2 v2 : R) (b2 B2 : float radix2),

hombnd m M u2 v2 b2 B2 ->
hombnd m M (u1 + u2) (v1 + v2) (Fplus b1 b2)
  (Fplus B1 B2)

Hprec:Prec_gt_0 prec

u2, v2:R

H12:(1 <= F2R B1)%R
H1:(Bmin <= m)%R ->
(Rabs (u1 - v1) <= F2R b1 * M)%R /\
(Rabs v1 <= F2R B1 * M)%R
H21:(0 <= F2R b2)%R
H22:(1 <= F2R B2)%R
H2:(Bmin <= m)%R ->
(Rabs (u2 - v2) <= F2R b2 * M)%R /\
(Rabs v2 <= F2R B2 * M)%R
hombnd m M (u1 + u2) (v1 + v2) (Fplus b1 b2)
  (Fplus B1 B2)

  Fplus (Fplus (Fmult b1 B2) (Fmult B1 b2)) (@Fmult radix2 b1 b2).

Definition round_err b B :=
  Fplus (Fmult (Fplus b B) (Float radix2 1 (- prec))) b.


emin, prec:Z
Hprec:Prec_gt_0 prec
forall (m M u v : R) (b B : float radix2),
hombnd m M u v b B ->
hombnd (Rmin m M) M (round radix2 fexp ZnearestE u) v
  (round_err b B) B

  (round_err b B) B

End Theory.

Section Example.

Definition fxp := FLT_exp (-1074) 53.
Definition add x y := round radix2 fxp ZnearestE (x + y).
Definition sub x y := round radix2 fxp ZnearestE (x - y).
Definition mul x y := round radix2 fxp ZnearestE (x * y).

Definition hombnd' := hombnd (-1074) 53.


forall u v : R,
generic_format radix2 fxp u ->
generic_format radix2 fxp v ->
hombnd' (Bmin (-1074) 53) (Rabs (u - v)) (sub u v)
  (u - v) {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := -53 |}
  {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := 0 |}


forall u v : R,
generic_format radix2 fxp u ->
generic_format radix2 fxp v ->
hombnd' (Bmin (-1074) 53) (Rabs (u - v)) (sub u v)
  (u - v) {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := -53 |}
  {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := 0 |}


u, v:R
Fu:generic_format radix2 fxp u
Fv:generic_format radix2 fxp v
hombnd' (Bmin (-1074) 53) (Rabs (u - v)) (sub u v)
  (u - v) {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := -53 |}
  {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := 0 |}


u, v:R
Fu:generic_format radix2 fxp u
Fv:generic_format radix2 fxp v
(0 <= F2R {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := -53 |})%R
u, v:R
Fu:generic_format radix2 fxp u
Fv:generic_format radix2 fxp v
(1 <= F2R {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := 0 |})%R /\
((Bmin (-1074) 53 <= Bmin (-1074) 53)%R ->
 (Rabs (sub u v - (u - v)) <=
  F2R {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := -53 |} * Rabs (u - v))%R /\
 (Rabs (u - v) <=
  F2R {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := 0 |} * Rabs (u - v))%R)


u, v:R
Fu:generic_format radix2 fxp u
Fv:generic_format radix2 fxp v
(1 <= F2R {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := 0 |})%R /\
((Bmin (-1074) 53 <= Bmin (-1074) 53)%R ->
 (Rabs (sub u v - (u - v)) <=
  F2R {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := -53 |} * Rabs (u - v))%R /\
 (Rabs (u - v) <=
  F2R {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := 0 |} * Rabs (u - v))%R)


u, v:R
Fu:generic_format radix2 fxp u
Fv:generic_format radix2 fxp v
(1 <= 1 * 1)%R /\
((Bmin (-1074) 53 <= Bmin (-1074) 53)%R ->
 (Rabs (sub u v - (u - v)) <=
  F2R {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := -53 |} * Rabs (u - v))%R /\
 (Rabs (u - v) <= 1 * 1 * Rabs (u - v))%R)


u, v:R
Fu:generic_format radix2 fxp u
Fv:generic_format radix2 fxp v
(1 <= 1)%R /\
((Bmin (-1074) 53 <= Bmin (-1074) 53)%R ->
 (Rabs (sub u v - (u - v)) <=
  F2R {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := -53 |} * Rabs (u - v))%R /\
 (Rabs (u - v) <= Rabs (u - v))%R)


u, v:R
Fu:generic_format radix2 fxp u
Fv:generic_format radix2 fxp v
H:(Bmin (-1074) 53 <= Bmin (-1074) 53)%R
(Rabs (sub u v - (u - v)) <=
 F2R {| Fnum := 1; Fexp := -53 |} * Rabs (u - v))%R


u, v:R
Fu:generic_format radix2 fxp u
Fv:generic_format radix2 fxp v
H:(Bmin (-1074) 53 <= Bmin (-1074) 53)%R

Definition orient2d x1 y1 x2 y2 x3 y3 :=
  sub (mul (sub x1 x3) (sub y2 y3)) (mul (sub x2 x3) (sub y1 y3)).

Definition orient2d_exact x1 y1 x2 y2 x3 y3 :=
  ((x1 - x3) * (y2 - y3) - (x2 - x3) * (y1 - y3))%R.

Definition norm2d x y := Rmax (Rabs x) (Rabs y).


forall x1 y1 x2 y2 x3 y3 : R,
generic_format radix2 fxp x1 ->
generic_format radix2 fxp y1 ->
generic_format radix2 fxp x2 ->
generic_format radix2 fxp y2 ->
generic_format radix2 fxp x3 ->
generic_format radix2 fxp y3 ->
let M :=
  (norm2d (x1 - x3) (x2 - x3) *
   norm2d (y1 - y3) (y2 - y3))%R in
hombnd' M M (orient2d x1 y1 x2 y2 x3 y3)
  (orient2d_exact x1 y1 x2 y2 x3 y3)
  {|
  Fnum := 5846006549323612646370400306145384485685829828610;
  Fexp := -212 |} {| Fnum := 2; Fexp := 0 |}

forall x y z : R,
Rmax x (Rmax y z) = Rmax (Rmax x y) z


forall x y z : R,
Rmax x (Rmax y z) = Rmax (Rmax x y) z


x, y, z:R
Rmax x (Rmax y z) = Rmax (Rmax x y) z


x, y, z:R
(if Rle_dec x (if Rle_dec y z then z else y)
 then if Rle_dec y z then z else y
 else x) =
(if Rle_dec (if Rle_dec x y then y else x) z
 then z
 else if Rle_dec x y then y else x)


x, y, z:R
Hxy:(x <= y)%R
(if Rle_dec x (if Rle_dec y z then z else y)
 then if Rle_dec y z then z else y
 else x) = (if Rle_dec y z then z else y)
x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
(if Rle_dec x (if Rle_dec y z then z else y)
 then if Rle_dec y z then z else y
 else x) = (if Rle_dec x z then z else x)


x, y, z:R
Hxy:(x <= y)%R
Hyz:(y <= z)%R
(if Rle_dec x z then z else x) = z
x, y, z:R
Hxy:(x <= y)%R
Hyz:~ (y <= z)%R
(if Rle_dec x y then y else x) = y
x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
(if Rle_dec x (if Rle_dec y z then z else y)
 then if Rle_dec y z then z else y
 else x) = (if Rle_dec x z then z else x)


x, y, z:R
Hxy:(x <= y)%R
Hyz:(y <= z)%R
Hxz:(x <= z)%R
(if Rle_dec x z then z else x) = z
x, y, z:R
Hxy:(x <= y)%R
Hyz:~ (y <= z)%R
(if Rle_dec x y then y else x) = y
x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
(if Rle_dec x (if Rle_dec y z then z else y)
 then if Rle_dec y z then z else y
 else x) = (if Rle_dec x z then z else x)


x, y, z:R
Hxy:(x <= y)%R
Hyz:~ (y <= z)%R
(if Rle_dec x y then y else x) = y
x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
(if Rle_dec x (if Rle_dec y z then z else y)
 then if Rle_dec y z then z else y
 else x) = (if Rle_dec x z then z else x)


x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
(if Rle_dec x (if Rle_dec y z then z else y)
 then if Rle_dec y z then z else y
 else x) = (if Rle_dec x z then z else x)


x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
Hyz:(y <= z)%R
(if Rle_dec x z then z else x) =
(if Rle_dec x z then z else x)
x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
Hyz:~ (y <= z)%R
(if Rle_dec x y then y else x) =
(if Rle_dec x z then z else x)


x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
Hyz:~ (y <= z)%R
(if Rle_dec x y then y else x) =
(if Rle_dec x z then z else x)


x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
Hyz:~ (y <= z)%R
~ (x <= y)%R -> x = (if Rle_dec x z then z else x)


x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
Hyz:~ (y <= z)%R
x = (if Rle_dec x z then z else x)


x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
Hyz:~ (y <= z)%R
(x <= z)%R -> x = z


x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
Hyz:~ (y <= z)%R
Hxz:(x <= z)%R
x = z


x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
Hyz:~ (y <= z)%R
Hxz:(x <= z)%R
(x <= y)%R


x, y, z:R
Hxy:~ (x <= y)%R
Hyz:~ (y <= z)%R
Hxz:(x <= z)%R
(z <= y)%R


x, y, z:R

Hyz:~ (y <= z)%R
Hxz:(x <= z)%R
(z < y)%R

now apply Rnot_le_lt.
Qed.


forall x y : R, Rmin (Rmin x y) (Rmax x y) = Rmin x y


forall x y : R, Rmin (Rmin x y) (Rmax x y) = Rmin x y


x, y:R
Rmin (Rmin x y) (Rmax x y) = Rmin x y


x, y:R
(Rmin x y <= Rmax x y)%R


x, y:R
(Rmin x y <= x)%R
x, y:R
(x <= Rmax x y)%R


x, y:R
(x <= Rmax x y)%R

apply Rmax_l.
Qed.


forall x y : R, Rmin (Rmin x y) y = Rmin x y


forall x y : R, Rmin (Rmin x y) y = Rmin x y


x, y:R
Rmin (Rmin x y) y = Rmin x y


x, y:R
(Rmin x y <= y)%R

apply Rmin_r.
Qed.

Definition incircle2d x1 y1 x2 y2 x3 y3 x4 y4 :=
  let X1 := sub x1 x4 in
  let X2 := sub x2 x4 in
  let X3 := sub x3 x4 in
  let Y1 := sub y1 y4 in
  let Y2 := sub y2 y4 in
  let Y3 := sub y3 y4 in
  let Z1 := add (mul X1 X1) (mul Y1 Y1) in
  let Z2 := add (mul X2 X2) (mul Y2 Y2) in
  let Z3 := add (mul X3 X3) (mul Y3 Y3) in
  add (add
    (mul (sub (mul X1 Y2) (mul X2 Y1)) Z3)
    (mul (sub (mul X2 Y3) (mul X3 Y2)) Z1))
    (mul (sub (mul X3 Y1) (mul X1 Y3)) Z2).

Definition incircle2d_exact x1 y1 x2 y2 x3 y3 x4 y4 :=
 (let X1 := x1 - x4 in
  let X2 := x2 - x4 in
  let X3 := x3 - x4 in
  let Y1 := y1 - y4 in
  let Y2 := y2 - y4 in
  let Y3 := y3 - y4 in
  let Z1 := X1 * X1 + Y1 * Y1 in
  let Z2 := X2 * X2 + Y2 * Y2 in
  let Z3 := X3 * X3 + Y3 * Y3 in
  (X1 * Y2 - X2 * Y1) * Z3 +
  (X2 * Y3 - X3 * Y2) * Z1 +
  (X3 * Y1 - X1 * Y3) * Z2)%R.

Definition norm3d x y z := Rmax (Rmax (Rabs x) (Rabs y)) (Rabs z).


forall x1 y1 x2 y2 x3 y3 x4 y4 : R,
generic_format radix2 fxp x1 ->
generic_format radix2 fxp y1 ->
generic_format radix2 fxp x2 ->
generic_format radix2 fxp y2 ->
generic_format radix2 fxp x3 ->
generic_format radix2 fxp y3 ->
generic_format radix2 fxp x4 ->
generic_format radix2 fxp y4 ->
let Nx := norm3d (x1 - x4) (x2 - x4) (x3 - x4) in
let Ny := norm3d (y1 - y4) (y2 - y4) (y3 - y4) in
let M := (Nx * Ny * Rmax Nx¬≤ Ny¬≤)%R in
let m := Rmin (Rmin Nx¬≤ Ny¬≤) M in
hombnd' m M (incircle2d x1 y1 x2 y2 x3 y3 x4 y4)
  (incircle2d_exact x1 y1 x2 y2 x3 y3 x4 y4)

  Fexp := -583 |} {| Fnum := 12; Fexp := 0 |}
